text: Olga Alekseyevna Nikitina (; born 26 November 1998) is a Russian sabre fencer and team world (2019) and European (2019) champion. ==Career== Nikitina was part of the gold medal winning team at the 2019 World Fencing Championships held in Budapest, Hungary.2019 World Fencing Championships ranking ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Russian sabre fencers Category:Russian female fencers
